  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(20 mins)</title>

  <p>[@@@@@@@@@] Ask students to work with their partner. Each partner writes a number that is in fraction or decimal form. Have them choose one number to be the coefficient in an equation of the form <m>px = q</m> and the second number the quantity on the other side of the equal sign. They then work together to write and evaluate the solution of the equation. Complete multiple rounds as time allows.</p>

</subsubsection>



